Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-對不起休息日找你\n-不 我以為會更早的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那件事很重要\n-交易的客戶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸誘了 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難 不過很期待結果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-特地來看看 -沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但是你們兩個不錯啊\n-才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-多虧了部長\n-我什麼都沒做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這個請收下恭喜你生孩子\n-這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒打算喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家有人喜歡喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工薪階層的中午很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那我去準備\n-不用了 不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别客氣啊\n-沒關條的 你們想喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自天喝酒好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天為了慶祝我生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公的部下來看望我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很脹呢 弄出來一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子經常喝奶水\n可能我奶水很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候非常難受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是廁所是廚房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來廚房我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:03:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無防備的被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後過了幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(老公的部下弄我的奶頭)\n母乳止不住的流出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(西野美幸主演上司妻子)\NJUY686
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公東西忘了帶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我混亂了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-對不起\n-沒事的 正好來銷售的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是在照顧孩子的話\n我就幫忙送過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-孩子在睡覺嗎\n-是的今天特别吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才喂完奶才終於睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是嗎 -不過還是很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎麼了嗎 -沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行佐野 住手 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 幹嘛 不行不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這是母乳嗎\n-不要 不要啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-太太 你很敏感嗎\n不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很硬呢\n-不要啊 不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 不要啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要 -好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要啊 -母乳 出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你看 -不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不要 住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手 不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這裡 這裡 -不要 不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 拜託了 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 拜託了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 奶子都可以高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續奶子露出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的 對 慢慢的 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子 慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩擦奶頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多弄些母乳出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我多弄一些 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我擼管 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 好多母乳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 給我擼管 很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太今天我要回去了\n下次繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 我先拍幾張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼太太 下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本我奶子就敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和那時候沒法比的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加的有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 在老公的客廳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被做了那種事情 我居然有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止這樣 我還想要同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:17:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 想要比那個更刺激的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有拒絕的自信\n就這樣等待佐野到來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然緊張 不過很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-住手 拜託了\n-沒事的 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 孌得好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 要變得很奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經放鬆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也摸摸我吧 想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 興奮了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.04,0:25:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.11,0:26:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.61,0:26:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.63,0:27:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.94,0:27:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要嗎 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.66,0:27:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.97,0:27:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.88,0:28:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在享受我的肉棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.33,0:29:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便動吧 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.23,0:29:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.74,0:29:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.25,0:29:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 高潮了 高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.57,0:29:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.79,0:30:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.80,0:30:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次轉過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.45,0:31:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要拔出來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.35,0:31:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.88,0:31:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.80,0:32:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 繼續繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.60,0:32:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常舒服呢 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.53,0:32:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 動起來 自己動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.64,0:32:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.08,0:33:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.48,0:33:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續動起來 別停
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.22,0:34:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.64,0:34:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下來吧 對
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.35,0:34:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真色啊 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.90,0:35:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.21,0:35:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.33,0:37:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服嗎 舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.36,0:38:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.78,0:40:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道 這樣不好 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.13,0:41:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻與我的想法相反的\n我的身體在期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.13,0:41:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.04,0:41:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一過後
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.64,0:41:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一遇後
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.34,0:41:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一過後
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.72,0:42:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.02,0:42:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我帶了有趣的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.53,0:42:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.44,0:42:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.94,0:42:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.77,0:43:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
