Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.32,1:29:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不行了\n-高潮了嗎 舒服嗎 太太
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.72,1:29:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.93,1:29:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.04,1:29:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣把腿打開
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.95,1:30:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.96,1:30:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.98,1:30:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 小穴舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.09,1:30:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常刺激呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.11,1:31:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊 很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.22,1:31:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又兩根哦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.73,1:31:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶頭都硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.34,1:31:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面好緊呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.25,1:31:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡是最舒服的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.26,1:31:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.47,1:32:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩擦奶頭怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.99,1:32:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了 高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.90,1:32:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.20,1:32:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你一個好東西 想看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.71,1:32:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色鬼 在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.62,1:32:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在看這裡吧 想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.43,1:33:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.04,1:33:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣想摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.44,1:33:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好大 -和誰比
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.85,1:33:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大 自己說出來
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.86,1:33:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡大肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.97,1:33:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你老公誰大
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.87,1:33:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來 不然不給你看 誰的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.28,1:33:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個更大
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.79,1:34:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔舔看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.02,1:34:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含住兩根怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.63,1:34:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好吃嗎 -好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.64,1:34:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-比部長的好吃吧\n-好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.95,1:34:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好厲害 -怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.45,1:35:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太該不會\n第一次見這麼大的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.56,1:35:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.37,1:35:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-第一次看 -想試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.87,1:35:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.58,1:35:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想試試嗎 那麼可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.48,1:35:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼太太
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.69,1:35:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你喜歡的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.09,1:35:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁没翹起來 趴下來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.90,1:35:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊 對對 說弄我屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.91,1:35:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.11,1:36:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-插我吧 -繼續說
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.02,1:36:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.43,1:36:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再說一次可以嗎\n拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.24,1:36:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？插入什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.34,1:36:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說的話不會給你的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.35,1:36:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來吧 什麼插入哪裡
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.06,1:36:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肉棒插入小穴吧 告訴我\n不然就直接插入了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.77,1:36:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.37,1:37:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是龜頭進去了哦 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.89,1:37:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.69,1:37:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大的進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.99,1:37:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.80,1:37:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了嗎 和部長誰的舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.50,1:37:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-誰的舒服 -這個
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.91,1:37:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個更舒服嗎 太太
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.31,1:37:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的肉棒 進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.85,1:38:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.75,1:38:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜歡的肉棒 不要停下
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.27,1:38:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了 高潮了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.78,1:38:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就高潮了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.89,1:38:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.50,1:39:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 這邊還有肉棒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.81,1:39:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對 很好
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.55,1:39:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害真騷
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.17,1:40:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.88,1:40:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣太太 看這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.29,1:40:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後繼續舔肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.09,1:40:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好 非常舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.20,1:40:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊還有呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.51,1:40:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.72,1:41:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.52,1:41:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.24,1:41:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 繼續自己動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.46,1:42:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常主動呢
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.37,1:42:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太很喜歡肉棒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.39,1:42:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太舒服嗎 給你看看下面
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.39,1:42:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開 自己看看吧 很色
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.10,1:42:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.60,1:42:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.21,1:42:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看到了插入的地方嗎\n-舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.62,1:43:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-舒服嗎 -舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.44,1:43:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太真的很色呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.24,1:43:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很深入哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.16,1:43:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面站起來 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.87,1:43:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手放鬆 對對很好
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.39,1:44:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 太太
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.60,1:44:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.66,1:45:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.21,1:46:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎麼樣太太 -很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.53,1:46:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.44,1:46:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.85,1:47:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面好多水呢 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.76,1:47:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了很多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.76,1:47:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.48,1:47:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 舔舔小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.71,1:48:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太可以坐上來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.51,1:48:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在肉棒上面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.12,1:48:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.62,1:48:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜歡的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.73,1:48:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己放入嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.94,1:48:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的别客氣 隨便動
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.75,1:48:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸自己的奶子 動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.86,1:49:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好厲害呢 -繼續動起來
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.97,1:49:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續給我喝
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.71,1:49:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好騷的動作呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.71,1:50:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的肉棒舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.94,1:50:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.95,1:50:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好騷呢 放屁的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.97,1:51:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊還有呢 太太 含住吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.08,1:51:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.19,1:51:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種機會很少吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.61,1:51:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續動起來 不要高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.25,1:52:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好騷呢
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.57,1:52:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.90,1:53:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真色啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.33,1:53:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要射了 -高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.49,1:55:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 變得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.39,1:55:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-變得很奇怪嗎 -不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.30,1:55:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.90,1:55:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.61,1:55:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可以射嗎 -變得好奇怪啊\n不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.64,1:55:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了 高潮了 不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.46,1:56:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.76,1:56:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行 高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.31,1:57:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天開始3P的關系開始了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.52,1:57:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起老公 但是
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.33,1:57:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天後
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.63,1:57:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.17,1:57:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.47,1:58:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.88,1:58:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-母乳出來了很多呢\n是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.88,1:58:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直在忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.79,1:58:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-為什麼\n-一個孩子很可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.69,1:58:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.99,1:58:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.50,1:58:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.50,1:58:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實的意思
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.61,1:58:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.91,1:58:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說我非常敏感
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.12,1:58:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西野美幸主演

